OL,3,CCalls for Port Talbot steelworks to be
OL,4,Crenationalised
OL,6,FWelsh Conservative Tom Giffard said he
OL,7,Fwas "optimistic about the town and
OL,8,Fwhat its future could look like",
OL,9,Fthanks to UK government investment.
OL,11,FTata Steel announced on 19 January it
OL,12,Fwould close Port Talbot's two blast
OL,13,Ffurnaces.
OL,15,FSince then a storm has erupted,
OL,16,Ftesting devolution and political
OL,17,Frelationships in Cardiff and
OL,18,FWestminster.
