OL,3,CCalls for Port Talbot steelworks to be
OL,4,Crenationalised
OL,6,FLuke Fletcher said: "For those of us
OL,7,Fin postindustrial communities,
OL,8,Frenationalisation is not a foreign
OL,9,Fconcept.
OL,11,F"Look at Tower Colliery in the 50s,
OL,12,Fwhich subsequently in 1994 was bought
OL,13,Fout by the workers - the only deep
OL,14,Fmine to survive the wave of closures.
OL,16,F"If you want a steel-specific example,
OL,17,Flook at the Basque Country where
OL,18,Fcooperative steel thrives and
OL,19,Funderpins a successful industry."
