OL,6,FOn Tuesday 23 January, the leader in
OL,7,Fthe Senedd, Andrew RT Davies diverged
OL,8,Ffrom his party's official line that
OL,9,Fthere is no alternative to the current
OL,10,Fplan.
OL,12,F"I disagree with that proposal," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"From the conversations I've had with
OL,16,FTata. I was always under the
OL,17,Fimpression that at least one of those
OL,18,Fblast furnaces would continue in
OL,19,Foperation.
