OL,6,FTom Giffard praised the UK government
OL,7,Ffor their investment, saying "not one
OL,8,Fsingle penny has been put in by the
OL,9,FWelsh government`not one penny."
OL,11,FAdding: "Where has the government
OL,12,Fbeen?"
OL,14,FThe Welsh government said it wants to
OL,15,Fsee one of the blast furnaces remain
OL,16,Fopen while the electric arc furnace is
OL,17,Finstalled.
OL,19,FWelsh Economy Minister said "there is
OL,20,Fan alternative that I'll go on to
OL,21,Fdescribe and discuss again".
